'''板鳃亞綱'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|Elasmobranchii}}）屬於[[软骨鱼纲|软骨鱼纲]]，包括[[鯊魚|鯊魚]]和[[鳐总目|鰩]]。鱼[[鳃|鳃]]是板状，鳃裂 5-7 对，鳃间隔宽大。体外是盾[[鳞|鳞]]或光滑，雄性腹鳍转化为[[鰭足|鰭足]]，沒有[[魚鰾|魚鰾]]，仰賴富含油脂的魚肝維持浮力。

最早的板鰓亞綱公认化石發現於[[志留紀|志留紀]]，現存大部分的[[目_(生物)|目]]多在[[侏儸紀|侏儸紀]]之后出現。許多早期种类在[[二疊紀|二疊紀]]末期中絕種，也因此導致在[[侏儸紀|侏儸紀]]時發生[[輻射適應|輻射適應]]。

==描述==
板鰓亞綱為[[軟骨魚綱|軟骨魚綱]]下的兩個亞綱之一，另一個為[[全頭亞綱|全頭亞綱]]（[[銀鮫|銀鮫]]）。鳃裂 5-7 对，体外是盾[[鳞|鳞]]，沒有[[魚鰾|魚鰾]]，眼睛具有[[脈絡膜層|脈絡膜層]]，雄性腹鰭特化為[[鰭足|鰭足]]。板鰓亞綱遍佈於[[熱帶|熱帶]]與[[溫帶|溫帶]]的水域中<ref>{{cite book |
last = Bigelow| first = Henry B. |
authorlink = Henry Bryant Bigelow|author2=Schroeder, William C.|author2-link=Schroeder, William C.  |
title = Fishes of the Western North Atlantic |
publisher = Sears Foundation for Marine Research, Yale University |
year = 1948 |
pages = 64–65 |
asin = B000J0D9X6}}</ref>。

許多魚類仰賴[[魚鰾|魚鰾]]維持浮力，但沒有魚鰾的板鰓亞綱物種則透過富含油脂的魚肝來維持浮力<ref>Oguri, M (1990) [http://spo.nwr.noaa.gov/tr90opt.pdf  "A review of selected physiological characteristics unique to elasmobranchs"] {{Wayback|url=http://spo.nwr.noaa.gov/tr90opt.pdf |date=20130218135249 }} In: ''Elasmobranchs as living resources: advances in the biology, ecology, systematics and the status of the fisheries'', eds. J. H. L. Pratt, S. H. Gruber and T. Taniuchi, US Department of Commerce, NOAA technical report NMFS 90, pp.49–54.</ref>。這些油脂在食物短少時也能作為暫時的營養來源<ref name=Hoenig1990>Hoenig, J.M. and Gruber, S.H. (1990) [http://spo.nwr.noaa.gov/tr90opt.pdf "Life-history patterns in the elasmobranchs: implications for fisheries management"] {{Wayback|url=http://spo.nwr.noaa.gov/tr90opt.pdf |date=20130218135249 }} In: ''Elasmobranchs as living resources: advances in the biology, ecology, systematics and the status of the fisheries'', eds. J. H. L. Pratt, S. H. Gruber and T. Taniuchi, US Department of Commerce, NOAA technical report NMFS 90, pp.1–16.</ref><ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1017/S0025315400038017 |title=The density of elasmobranchs |journal=Journal of the Marine Biological Association of the United Kingdom |volume=49 |issue=4 |pages=913 |year=2009 |last1=Bone |first1=Q. |last2=Roberts |first2=B. L. }}</ref>。其中深海鯊魚的肝重量可達體重 20%<ref name=Vannuccini2002>Vannuccini, Stefania (2002) [http://www.fao.org/docrep/005/x3690e/x3690e0r.htm Shark liver oil products] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fao.org/docrep/005/x3690e/x3690e0r.htm |date=20130626203527 }} In: ''Shark Utilization, Marketing and Trade'', Fisheries Technical paper 389, FAO, Rome. {{ISBN|92-5-104361-2}}.</ref>，常被視為是漁業捕獲的目標。

==演化歷程==
板鰓亞綱的出現最早可追溯至[[奧陶紀|奧陶紀]]（4.5 - 4.2 億年前），遠在陸生[[脊椎動物|脊椎動物]]與陸生植物之前<ref name="RQGT">{{cite web|last=Martin|first=R. Aidan|url=http://www.elasmo-research.org/education/evolution/geologic_time.htm|title=Geologic Time|publisher=ReefQuest|accessdate=2006-09-09|archive-date=2019-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191021190340/http://www.elasmo-research.org/education/evolution/geologic_time.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，然而因為只有發現到部分鱗片的化石，因此部分科學家並不認為是鯊魚而是[[無頜總綱|無頜總綱]]的{{link-en|小瘤魚類|thelodont}}<ref name="RQES">{{cite web |last=Martin |first=R. Aidan |url=http://www.elasmo-research.org/education/evolution/earliest.htm |title=The Earliest Sharks |publisher=ReefQuest |accessdate=2009-02-10 |archive-date=2008-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081223011855/http://www.elasmo-research.org/education/evolution/earliest.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。目前最早認為屬於鯊魚的化石來自於 4.2 億年前的[[志留紀|志留紀]]<ref name="RQES"/>，外型與現今的鯊魚外型差異很大<ref name="RQA"/>，這個時期所發現的牙齒上有多個尖銳突起，外型類似[[三叉戟|三叉戟]]，適合用來捕捉魚類。

[[裂口鯊|裂口鯊]]（''Cladoselache''）出現於 3.7 億年前<ref name="RQA">{{cite web |last=Martin |first=R. Aidan |url=http://www.elasmo-research.org/education/evolution/ancient.htm |title=Ancient Sharks |publisher=ReefQuest |accessdate=2006-09-09 |archive-date=2012-12-18 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Czf9hGGw?url=http://www.elasmo-research.org/education/evolution/ancient.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，化石發現於[[美國|美國]]的[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]]、[[肯塔基州|肯塔基州]]及[[田納西州|田納西州]]，在當時[[北美洲|北美洲]]仍然為一片汪洋。裂口鯊的體長僅約{{convert|1.8|m|ft}}，具有三角形的魚鰭和狹窄的顎<ref name="RQA" />。裂口鯊的牙齒化石並沒有很多，相信可能是因為牠們的牙齒替換速率並不如現代鯊魚那般頻繁。牠們的[[尾鰭|尾鰭]]形狀與[[大白鯊|大白鯊]]、[[尖吻鯖鯊|尖吻鯖鯊]]和[[長鰭鯖鯊|長鰭鯖鯊]]類似。從獵物在裂口鯊胃中的方向可推估牠們也是靈活快速的[[掠食者|掠食者]]。

在[[石炭紀|石炭紀]]時，{{link-en|異刺鯊目|Xenacanthida}}兴起（包括[[異刺鯊|異刺鯊]]），幾乎只生活在[[淡水|淡水]]水域之中<ref>[http://hoopermuseum.earthsci.carleton.ca/sharks/P2-3.htm "Xenacanth"] {{Wayback|url=http://hoopermuseum.earthsci.carleton.ca/sharks/P2-3.htm |date=20070107033634 }}. Hooper Virtual Natural History Museum. Retrieved on 11/26/06.</ref><ref>[http://www.elasmo-research.org/education/evolution/earliest.htm "Biology of Sharks and Rays: 'The Earliest Sharks'"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.elasmo-research.org/education/evolution/earliest.htm |date=20081223011855 }}. Retrieved on 11/26/06.</ref>，並且成功散佈至世界各地，牠們在約 2.2 億年前滅絕。另一群為{{link-en|弓鮫目|Hybodontiformes}}（包括[[弓鮫|弓鮫]]）則生活在海洋中。在 3.25 億年前一具幾乎完整的鯊魚鰓部化石顯示鯊魚並非[[活化石|活化石]]，在這幾億年來其器官早已因為演化而產生很大的變化<ref>{{Cite journal |last1=Pradel |first1=A. |last2=Maisey |first2=J. G. |last3=Tafforeau |first3=P. |last4=Mapes |first4=R. H. |last5=Mallatt |first5=J. |year=2014 |title=A Palaeozoic shark with osteichthyan-like branchial arches |url=http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/vaop/ncurrent/full/nature13195.html |journal=[[Nature_(journal)|Nature]] |volume=509 |issue=7502 |pages=608–611 |doi=10.1038/nature13195 |pmid=24739974 |bibcode=2014Natur.509..608P }}</ref>。

其他板鰓亞綱动物在[[侏儸紀|侏儸紀]]時產生第二次的[[輻射適應|輻射適應]]，鰩和魟也約在這個時期出現。現存大部分的[[目_(生物)|目]]在[[侏儸紀|侏儸紀]]之后出現<ref name=EoDP>{{cite book |editor1-last=Palmer |editor1-first=D. |year=1999 |title=The Marshall Illustrated Encyclopedia of Dinosaurs and Prehistoric Animals |publisher=Marshall Editions |location=London |page=26 |isbn=1-84028-152-9 }}</ref>。
==分类==
本亚纲现存种类主要有两大类：鲨类和鳐类，分为如下各目：

*[[鲨总目|鲨总目]] Selachimorpha
**[[六鳃鲨目|六鳃鲨目]] Hexanchiformes
**[[虎鲨目|虎鲨目]] Heterodontiformes
**[[鬚鮫目|鬚鮫目]] Orectolobiformes
**[[鼠鲨目|鼠鲨目]] Lamniformes
**[[真鲨目|真鲨目]] Carcharhiniformes（白眼鮫目）
**[[角鲨目|角鲨目]] Squaliformes
**[[扁鲨目|扁鲨目]] Squatiniformes
**[[锯鲨目|锯鲨目]] Pristiophoriformes
*[[鳐总目|鳐总目]] Batoidea（魟总目）
**[[鳐目|鳐目]] Rajiformes
**[[电鳐目|电鳐目]] Torpediniformes
**[[犁头鳐目|犁头鳐目]] Rhinopristiformes
**[[燕魟目|燕魟目]] Myliobatiformes

包括已灭绝种类的分类：

*†''Plesioselachus''
*†[[似扁鲨目|似扁鲨目]] Squatinactiformes
*†[[原尖齿鲨目|原尖齿鲨目]] Protacrodontiformes
*†[[裂口鲨总目|裂口鲨总目]] Cladoselachimorpha
**†[[裂口鲨目|裂口鲨目]] Cladoselachiformes
*†[[异棘鲨总目|异棘鲨总目]] Xenacanthimorpha
**†[[异棘鲨目|异棘鲨目]] Xenacanthiformes
*[[鲨鳐下纲|鲨鳐下纲]] Euselachii
**†[[栉棘鲨目|栉棘鲨目]] Ctenacanthiformes
**†[[弓鲛目|弓鲛目]] Hybodontiformes
**[[新鲨类|新鲨类]] Neoselachii
